Huhueteotl is the Olman god of fire and the motion of time. He is chaotic evil. He is always shown as a fire-shrouded, armor-clad humanoid with a reptilian, demonic head. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Deities &amp; Demigods (First Edition)        
              
                    Dragon magazine #283        
              
                    The Scarlet Brotherhood